	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Does anyone know the pitch of the pin inside the NES controller plug in? And if they can be bought?<br /><br />I tried a 1.15mm square post (too big) and the .65mm post was too small.<br /><br /><br />Thanks!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


