		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle">Markfrizb wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Does anyone know the pitch of the pin inside the NES controller plug in? And if they can be bought?<br /><br />I tried a 1.15mm square post (too big) and the .65mm post was too small.<br /><br /><br />Thanks!</div><br />What I used was a nice, kind of thick paperclip. It fit perfectly.<br />I am totally serious. I made a NES controller -&gt; USB controller adapter with paperclips and an arduino.

		

